trans-unit.source: Provides information about a type that components can access across application domain and process boundaries.
trans-unit.target: Gir informasjon om en type som har tilgang til komponenter på tvers av programmet domenet og behandle grenser.

trans-unit.source: The RemoteTypeData structure provides information about an object that implements the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract> interface.
trans-unit.target: Strukturen RemoteTypeData gir informasjon om et objekt som implementerer den <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract>grensesnittet.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract>

trans-unit.source: To get type information about a remote object, components call the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract.GetRemoteType%2A> method to obtain an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha informasjon om om et eksternt objekt kalle komponenter <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract.GetRemoteType%2A>metoden for å hente en <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract>.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract> </xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteObjectContract.GetRemoteType%2A>

trans-unit.source: Then, components call the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract.GetTypeData%2A> method to get a RemoteTypeData.
trans-unit.target: Deretter komponenter kall av <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract.GetTypeData%2A>metode for å få en RemoteTypeData.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.IRemoteTypeContract.GetTypeData%2A>

trans-unit.source: Indicates the rank (that is, the number of dimensions) of the remote array type that this <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteTypeData"></xref> describes.
trans-unit.target: Angir rangeringen (det vil si antall dimensjoner) for den eksterne matrisen typen som denne <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteTypeData"> </xref> beskriver.

trans-unit.source: To determine whether a <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteTypeData> describes an array, use the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteTypeData.IsArray> field.
trans-unit.target: Å finne ut om en <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteTypeData>beskriver en matrise, bruk av <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteTypeData.IsArray>felt.</xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteTypeData.IsArray> </xref:System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteTypeData>

trans-unit.source: Represents the name of the remote type that this <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteTypeData"></xref> describes, qualified by the name of the assembly that contains the type.
trans-unit.target: Representerer navnet på eksterne typen som denne <xref href="System.AddIn.Contract.Automation.RemoteTypeData"> </xref> beskriver, kvalifisert av navnet på samlingen som inneholder typen.

trans-unit.source: The assembly-qualified name of a type includes the name of the assembly from which the type was loaded.
trans-unit.target: Samlingen kvalifiserte navnet på en type inkluderer navnet på samlingen som typen ble lastet inn fra.

trans-unit.source: For more information about the format of an assembly-qualified name, see the <xref:System.Type.AssemblyQualifiedName%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om formatet på en kvalifisert samlingen av <xref:System.Type.AssemblyQualifiedName%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Type.AssemblyQualifiedName%2A?displayProperty=fullName>
